&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class="language-c&amp;#43;&amp;#43;"&gt;b[len]&amp;#61;a[i]; &lt;span class="hljs-regexp"&gt;//&lt;/span&gt;将a[i]的值&amp;#xff0c;赋值给b[len]
len&amp;#43;&amp;#43;;   &lt;span class="hljs-regexp"&gt;//&lt;/span&gt;然后将len加&lt;span class="hljs-number"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#xff0c;即是数组下标往后移动一位
&lt;span class="hljs-regexp"&gt;//&lt;/span&gt;b[len&amp;#43;&amp;#43;]&amp;#61;a[i];
&lt;span class="hljs-regexp"&gt;/*将a[i]的值&amp;#xff0c;赋值给b[len]后&amp;#xff0c;len再加1&amp;#xff1b;即上文中&amp;#xff0c;对于后&amp;#43;&amp;#43;&amp;#xff0c;如&amp;#xff1a;len&amp;#43;&amp;#43;&amp;#xff0c;变量len先操作后再进行加1&amp;#xff1b;*/&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;div class="post-text" itemprop="text"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;label&lt;/code&gt; attribute is used by some browsers to display the content of the option, so your list box might display two &lt;code&gt;0&lt;/code&gt; options.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A better solution might be to do the following:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;select id="category" name="data[cat]"&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;option value="12,0"&amp;gt;A&amp;lt;/option&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;option value="7,0"&amp;gt;B&amp;lt;/option&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/select&amp;gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and split the value in the event handler, e.g.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;$("#category").livequery('change', function () {            
    var values = ($(this)[0].value).split(",");
    var catId = values[0];
    var otherId = values[1];
});
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

