&lt;p&gt;Notice the cast to &lt;code&gt;int&lt;/code&gt; for the GET param.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You could also just cast to int and PHP will default to integer 0 if it's not already int:  &lt;/p&gt;

