&lt;hr&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Couldn't help myself - you can also use a ternary to make your setting of the &lt;code&gt;$pageNum&lt;/code&gt; cleaner (IMO):  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;$rowsPerPage = 20;

$pageNum = isset($_GET['page'])
