&lt;h1&gt;Another approaches&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do all the routing processing in PHP, not even using &lt;code&gt;.htaccess&lt;/code&gt; and then retrieve data for routing in JSON format. You'd access this from an Ajax request&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;jQuery.ajax({
